This paper discusses the use of epidemiological models to analyze the spread of computer malware, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also involves data analysis and modeling, which could fall under the categories of social and information networks (cs.SI), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
